node.title: Producers Guild Nominations Put ‘Dune’ in Play
node.alt: Timothee Chalamet and Rebecca Ferguson in “Dune,” the highest-grossing film to be nominated by the Producers Guild.
node.description: The group’s choices can influence what academy voters do at the Oscars. That’s why the omissions of “Spider-Man: No Way Home” and “No Time to Die” may be significant.
node.content: ["The Producers Guild on Thursday unveiled its nominations for the PGA Awards this year.
